(30, 4, '2009-12-09 04:30:36', 'Magento Preview Version 1.4.0.0-beta1 is now available', 'We are happy to announce the availability of Magento Preview Version 1.4.0.0-beta1 for download.\nAs this is a preview version it is NOT recommended in any way to be used in a production environment.', 'http://www.magentocommerce.com/blog/comments/magento-preview-version-1400-beta1-now-available/', 1, 1),
