(370, 4, '2013-05-28 04:43:12', 'Improve your shopping experience with Quick Shopping 1.2.0', 'Quick Shopping 1.2.0  is now available with next new features:\n\n- Templates and skin resources moved to base folder\n- Better compatibility with third-party themes\n- Highlight page support added\n- Updated styles for window and button\n- Layout xml optimization\n- Better javascript handling of response text\n- Amlanding integration added\n- QuickView button will be hidden if no css and js are loaded.', 'http://bit.ly/10Eoz3x', 0, 0),
