(457, 61, 'These handmade solid 14K yellow gold Maple Leaf cufflinks are a funky and sophisticated way to say you are proud to be Canadian! Maple Leaf Cufflinks make an ideal gift for Canadians living abroad, and they make a great gift for Canadians traveling abroad to bring to their hosts or clients. 2017 is Canada\'s sesquicentennial year, so these are a special way to show your Canadian pride for Canada\'s 150th birthday! Also available in white gold and sterling silver'),
