(14, 36, 0, 4, '<p>Getting engaged is one of the happiest and most romantic times of your life.  If a custom gemstone or diamond engagement ring is the next step for you on your journey together, breathe easy because Tamara can help you create a fantastic gemstone or diamond engagement ring that expresses your love and captures the essence of your relationship.  <a href=\"/contact\">Contact us</a> to arrange for a custom design consultation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Have a look at our <a href=\"/wedding/wedding-bands\">Wedding Bands</a> or <a href=\"/resources\">Learn More</a> about diamonds.</p>'),
