(44, 36, 0, 10, '<p>Corporate representatives and entrepreneurs of all kinds rely on <strong>Studio</strong>1098 to help them build their brands and show clients and employees that they really care. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you travel abroad to meet clients and want to show those clients that Canada has something to offer beyond maple syrup and icewine, consider taking our Maple Leaf Cufflnks as gifts instead and say goodbye to your worries about glass breaking in your luggage!  </p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have an employee recognition program, consider adding some <strong>Studio</strong>1098 pieces to your catalogue of employee gifts.  Or, engage us to make some exclusive, custom pieces for your organization. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Corporate successes do not have to be celebrated with cheesy plastic plaques and we find it a bit baffling that deals are closed with \"tombstones\".  Give us a chance to design a unique momento and we guarantee you\'ll never go back to celebrating with plastic again! </p>'),
