(95, 36, 0, 19, '<p>The jewellery featured on this page is all either one-of-a-kind, or one of a very limited series that we don\'t expect to make more than one or two of - ever.  Most include a unique gemstone, and all are red carpet worthy!</p>\r\n<p>So if you are looking for something truly unique or inspiration for a fabulous custom piece of your own, this page is a good starting point.    If you have a vision of a piece you\'d like made, please get in touch with Tamara at the studio or <a href=\"http://www.studio1098customjewellery.com/contact\" title=\"Schedule an Appointment\">click this link</a> to <a href=\"http://www.studio1098customjewellery.com/contact\" title=\"Schedule A Design Consultation\">schedule a design consultation</a>&nbsp;. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>If you are looking for something personalized that can incorporate a name, initials, your anniversary years or the number of years that you\'ve been together, check out our <a href=\"http://www.studio1098customjewellery.com/collections/personalized-jewellery-toronto\" title=\"Personalized Jewellery\">personalized collection</a>.</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://www.studio1098customjewellery.com/engagement/custom-diamond-engagement-rings-toronto\" title=\"Custom Gemstone and Diamond Engagement Rings\">Click this link</a> to browse the Studio1098 <a href=\"http://www.studio1098customjewellery.com/engagement/custom-diamond-engagement-rings-toronto\" title=\"Custom Diamond Engagement Rings\">custom gemstone and diamond engagement collections</a></p>'),
