(100, 36, 0, 20, '<p>We designed the jewellery in this collection so that you can add a personal touch!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Depending on the piece, these designs can incorporate names, initials, your anniversary dates, dates of birth, the number of years you\'ve been together, kids names, pets names, marathons you\'ve run, milestones you\'ve achieved, and really just about anything else you can come up with.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have an idea for a personalized piece of jewellery that you don\'t see here, please get in touch with us by <a title=\"Contact Tamara and Kathryn\" href=\"http://www.studio1098customjewellery.com/contact\">clicking this link</a> and we\'ll find a way to make it happen!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Of course, most of our designs not shown here can also be personalized with engraving or birthstones...</p>'),
