(120, 36, 0, 24, '<p>These Valentine\'s Day Gift Ideas were made with love just for you! What could be more romantic and thoughtful than a handmade gift? At Studio1098, personalized handmade custom jewellery that is as unique as your love is our specialty.</p>\r\n<p>Online orders placed by February 1, 2017 that specify store pick-up will be ready for pickup at our studio at 1098 Yonge Street by 2 p.m. on February 11, 2017. Orders to be shipped will be shipped via Canada Post on February 6 if ordered by January 29. If we cannot meet those deadlines (for production reasons), we will be in contact with you within 24 hours of plaing your order to discuss options.</p>\r\n<p>If you have an idea for a custom gift, or need to pick up your gift earlier than February 11 or have it shipped before February 6, please contact us by email to tamara@studio1098.com or come by the studio at 1098 Yonge Street! If you have any questions, let us know and we\'ll do our best to answer!</p>\r\n<p>Happy Valentine\'s Day!</p>'),
