(1569, 61, 0, 421, '<p>The sparkle of this princess cut diamond is amplified by a cushion-shaped halo.  The setting minimizes the amount of metal and includes engraving work on the sides to make the ring even more dazzling.</p>\r\n<p>This custom ring can be made in platinum, white gold, yellow gold, or rose gold.  The centre stone could be a diamond, coloured diamond, sapphire, ruby or other coloured stone, and the setting style can include the engraved work on the sides or some other style of setting.&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.studio1098customjewellery.com/engagement/custom-halo-engagement-rings\" title=\"Custom Halo Diamond Engagement Rings\">Click here to see other examples of Studio1098 Halo Engagement Rings</a>.  Please be in touch if you want to discuss the possibilities!</p>'),
