(1588, 61, 0, 430, '<p>The tapered baguettes in this sapphire engagement ring enhance the centre sapphire and give this ring an old-world antique feel.</p>\r\n<p>You can see an additional picture of this ring style with a diamond in the centre by clicking <a href=\"http://www.studio1098customjewellery.com/diamond-engagement-ring-tapered-baguettes-186\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Diamond Engagement Ring with Tapered Baguettes\">here</a>. &nbsp;This custom ring can be made in platinum, white gold, yellow gold or rose gold. &nbsp;</p>'),
(1589, 62, 0, 430, '<p>The tapered baguettes in this sapphire engagement ring enhance the centre sapphire and give this ring an old-world antique feel.</p>\r\n<p>You can see an additional picture of this ring style with a diamond in the centre by clicking <a href=\"http://www.studio1098customjewellery.com/diamond-engagement-ring-tapered-baguettes-186\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Diamond Engagement Ring with Tapered Baguettes\">here</a>. &nbsp;This custom ring can be made in platinum, white gold, yellow gold or rose gold. &nbsp;</p>'),
(1590, 61, 0, 431, '<p>The centre sapphire in this ring is flanked by two marquis-shaped diamonds, two rectangular baguettes, and a variety of round diamonds set in milgrained shapes.  Two square sapphires on each side of the ring complete the design.</p>\r\n<p>This is one of several rings in this <a href=\"http://www.studio1098customjewellery.com/blog/vintage-engagement-rings/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Vintage-Inspired Engagement Ring Blog Article\">vintage-inspired</a> series - Click&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.studio1098customjewellery.com/engagement/vintage-inspired-engagement-rings/vintage-inspired-engagement-ring-with-emerald-accents\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Art Deco Engagement Ring with Emerald Accents\">here</a>&nbsp;to see a centre European cut diamond with two emeralds on the side and <a href=\"http://www.studio1098customjewellery.com/engagement/vintage-inspired-engagement-rings/custom-vintage-sapphire-engagement-ring-oval\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Oval Sapphire Art Deco Engagement Ring\">here</a>&nbsp;for&nbsp;one with an oval sapphire in the centre.</p>'),
(1591, 62, 0, 431, '<p>The centre sapphire in this ring is flanked by two marquis-shaped diamonds, two rectangular baguettes, and a variety of round diamonds set in milgrained shapes.  Two square sapphires on each side of the ring complete the design.</p>\r\n<p>This is one of several rings in this <a href=\"http://www.studio1098customjewellery.com/blog/vintage-engagement-rings/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Vintage-Inspired Engagement Ring Blog Article\">vintage-inspired</a> series - Click&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.studio1098customjewellery.com/engagement/vintage-inspired-engagement-rings/vintage-inspired-engagement-ring-with-emerald-accents\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Art Deco Engagement Ring with Emerald Accents\">here</a>&nbsp;to see a centre European cut diamond with two emeralds on the side and <a href=\"http://www.studio1098customjewellery.com/engagement/vintage-inspired-engagement-rings/custom-vintage-sapphire-engagement-ring-oval\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Oval Sapphire Art Deco Engagement Ring\">here</a>&nbsp;for&nbsp;one with an oval sapphire in the centre.</p>'),
(1592, 61, 0, 432, 'These one-of-a-kind blue sapphire and diamond earrings are dramatic and  original.  \r\n\r\nThey\'re made of four sapphire slices surrounded with white diamond pavé, with two blue sapphire pavé circles in between.  \r\n\r\nThe total carat weight of the sapphires is over 27 carats, and there are approximately 0.61 carats of diamonds in the pavé.'),
(1593, 62, 0, 432, 'These one-of-a-kind blue sapphire and diamond earrings are dramatic and  original.  \r\n\r\nThey\'re made of four sapphire slices surrounded with white diamond pavé, with two blue sapphire pavé circles in between.  \r\n\r\nThe total carat weight of the sapphires is over 27 carats, and there are approximately 0.61 carats of diamonds in the pavé.'),
(1594, 61, 0, 433, 'The diamond and sapphire bows on these earrings perfectly balance the pear-shaped blue sapphire slices that hang from them.  \r\n\r\nThe sapphire slices have a total weight of approximately 37.98 carats and vary from blue to light blue. I love the ombre look the colour variation gives these earrings!  \r\n\r\nThe total diamond carat weight is approximately 0.25 carats.'),
(1595, 62, 0, 433, 'The diamond and sapphire bows on these earrings perfectly balance the pear-shaped blue sapphire slices that hang from them.  \r\n\r\nThe sapphire slices have a total weight of approximately 37.98 carats and vary from blue to light blue. I love the ombre look the colour variation gives these earrings!\r\n\r\nThe total diamond carat weight is approximately 0.25 carats.'),
(1596, 61, 0, 434, 'These earrings were custom designed for a client who was looking to make a splash at the numerous formal events she attends each year, but who also wanted a practical pair of good sapphire studs that she could wear every day.  \r\n\r\nAs a result, these earrings are each constructed in two parts - the cushion cut sapphire studs are removable and my client wears them frequently.  The top-quality, vibrant blue sapphires are natural, unheated sapphires from Sri Lanka.  \r\n\r\nThe jackets (the dangly parts) feature a pair of light blue sapphire slices, surrounded by pavé and bezel set diamonds, including a pair of pear-shaped diamonds.  \r\n\r\nAs a bonus, the earrings can also be worn with diamond studs.'),
(1597, 62, 0, 434, 'These earrings were custom designed for a client who was looking to make a splash at the numerous formal events she attends each year, but who also wanted a practical pair of good sapphire studs that she could wear every day.  \r\n\r\nAs a result, these earrings are each constructed in two parts - the cushion cut sapphire studs are removable and my client wears them frequently.  The top-quality, vibrant blue sapphires are natural, unheated sapphires from Sri Lanka.  \r\n\r\nThe jackets (the dangly parts) feature a pair of light blue sapphire slices, surrounded by pavé and bezel set diamonds, including a pair of pear-shaped diamonds.  \r\n\r\nAs a bonus, the earrings can also be worn with diamond studs.'),
(1598, 61, 0, 435, 'These unique large 14K white gold sapphire stud earrings feature rose-cut sapphire slices surrounded by pavé sapphires.  \r\n\r\nThe sapphire slices weigh approximately 26.2 carats, and the earrings measure about two centimetres in diameter overall. '),
(1599, 62, 0, 435, 'These unique large 14K white gold sapphire stud earrings feature rose-cut sapphire slices surrounded by pavé sapphires.  \r\n\r\nThe sapphire slices weigh approximately 26.2 carats, and the earrings measure about two centimetres in diameter overall. '),
