(1637, 61, 0, 453, 'The tags on this necklace are larger than the tags on our Sterling Silver Name Necklace With Swarovski Crystals.  The tags for the large necklace are approximately 6 mm wide and approximately 1.2-1.5 mm thick.  Instead of a Swarovski crystal to accent each tag, the necklace can be made with or without a cluster of crystals in between the tags.  The chain that comes with this necklace is also thicker than the one that comes with the smaller version.  \r\n\r\nAdditional tags and additional crystal clusters are $40 each.  A clear Swarovski crystal is included at the back of the necklace near the clasp (it looks great AND keeps the tags from falling off).\r\n\r\n<b>Step 1: Enter a name (or date) for each tag in English, French, Spanish or other language. Dates will appear in the following format: 02.26.87 (MM.DD.YY). If you are ordering a crystal cluster, don\'t forget to pick the colours.  '),
