(1645, 61, 0, 456, 'A client commissioned this custom platinum wedding ring for her fiancé so that she would always remember their proposal. \r\n\r\nThe mountains depicted on his ring are Mount Victoria on the left and Mount LeFroy on the right, which her fiancé has climbed. In the valley between the two mountain is a small building called Abbott Hut and where the proposal happened. It is at the BC-Alberta border of Yoho and Banff National Parks. How romantic!'),
(1646, 72, 0, 456, 'custom jewellery, platinum, mountain, mount lefroy, mount victoria, wedding, toronto, studio1098, blogTO,'),
(1647, 62, 0, 456, 'A client commissioned this custom platinum wedding ring for her fiancé so that she would always remember their proposal. \r\n\r\nThe mountains depicted on his ring are Mount Victoria on the left and Mount LeFroy on the right, which her fiancé has climbed. In the valley between the two mountain is a small building called Abbott Hut and where the proposal happened. It is at the BC-Alberta border of Yoho and Banff National Parks. How romantic!'),
(1648, 61, 0, 457, '<p>These handmade solid 14K yellow gold Maple Leaf cufflinks are a funky and sophisticated way to say you are proud to be Canadian!</p>\r\n<p>Maple Leaf Cufflinks make an ideal gift for Canadians living abroad, and they make a great gift for Canadians traveling abroad to bring to their hosts or clients.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">2017 is Canada\'s sesquicentennial year, so these are a special way to show your Canadian pride for Canada\'s 150th birthday!</span></p>\r\n\r\nAlso available in white gold and sterling silver'),
(1649, 72, 0, 457, 'maple leaf cufflinks, sterling silver cufflinks, 14K yellow gold cufflinks, Canada, sesquicentennial, handmade cufflinks, studio1098, toronto, canada'),
(1650, 62, 0, 457, 'These handmade solid 14K yellow gold Maple Leaf cufflinks are a funky and sophisticated way to say you are proud to be Canadian!\r\n\r\nMaple Leaf Cufflinks make an ideal gift for Canadians living abroad, and they make a great gift for Canadians traveling abroad to bring to their hosts or clients.\r\n\r\n2017 is Canada\'s sesquicentennial year, so these are a special way to show your Canadian pride for Canada\'s 150th birthday!'),
(1651, 61, 0, 458, 'RCA Music unveiled the 45 RPM record in 1949. The format was an instant hit. The 7\" inch records were cute, portable, inexpensive and colourful. Every music genre of music had its own colour of vinyl and popular releases were on standard black vinyl. Some kids traded hockey cards - we traded 45s. And they even had a \'B side\'! \r\n\r\n45\'s gave way to the \"Mix Tape Era\" in the early 1980\'s, but nostalgia for the 45 and the 45 adapter will forever live on in the hearts of music lovers the world over. Remember the 45? These cufflinks are for you!'),
(1652, 72, 0, 458, '45, rpm, centre, music, history, mix-tape, 1980\'s, handmade, sterling silver, cufflinks, cufflink, custom, jewellery, toronto, canada, gift, music lover, rock and roll, jukebox'),
(1653, 62, 0, 458, '45\'s gave way to the \"Mix Tape Era\" in the early 1980\'s, but nostalgia for the 45 and the 45 adapter will forever live on in the hearts of music lovers the world over. Remember the 45? These cufflinks are for you!'),
(1654, 61, 0, 459, 'The apple has captured our imagination like no other fruit. From Adam and Eve to Newton and his arrow, apples have figured prominently in the storytelling and lore of almost every culture. \r\n\r\nDo you have an apple for the teacher? Are you as American as apple pie? Do you compare apples and oranges? An apple a day keeps the doctor away. If you want apples, you have to shake the trees. Apples have a core, and so does every person. \r\n\r\nIs someone the apple of your eye? If so, these handmade sterling silver apple cufflinks will make the perfect gift. \r\n\r\nOne rotten apple may spoil the bunch, but our handmade sterling silver apples will never go bad. \r\n\r\nNow, how do you like them apples?'),
(1655, 72, 0, 459, 'apple, teacher, apple of my eye, handmade, sterling silver, cufflinks, apple pie, American, Canada, doctor, apple a day, gift, custom, jewellery, toronto\r\n\r\n'),
(1656, 62, 0, 459, 'Do you have an apple for the teacher? Are you as American as apple pie? Do you compare apples and oranges? An apple a day keeps the doctor away. Is someone the apple of your eye? If so, these handmade sterling silver apple cufflinks will make the perfect gift. '),
(1657, 61, 0, 460, 'Petrified wood forms in the earth when trees or tree-like plants are buried under sediment or volcanic ash. If this happens in an oxygen-free environment where mineral-laden water is present, then, over time, the tree may become a three-dimensional stone representation of its original structure. \r\n\r\nPetrified wood is one of my favourite gemstones because it is one of the only instances in nature where stone takes on the softer feel of organic material. It is truly wood frozen in time. \r\n\r\nEach piece of petrified wood is one of a kind - the bezels for these stones were hand-fabricated in my studio to make these cufflinks. '),
(1658, 72, 0, 460, 'Petrified wood forms in the earth when trees or tree-like plants are buried under sediment or volcanic ash. If this happens in an oxygen-free environment where mineral-laden water is present, then, over time, the tree may become a three-dimensional stone representation of its original structure. \r\n\r\nPetrified wood is one of my favourite gemstones because it is one of the only instances in nature where stone takes on the softer feel of organic material. It is truly wood frozen in time. \r\n\r\nEach piece of petrified wood is one of a kind - the bezels for these stones were hand-fabricated in my studio to make these cufflinks.'),
(1659, 62, 0, 460, 'Petrified wood is one of my favourite gemstones because it is one of the only instances in nature where stone takes on the softer feel of organic material. It is truly wood frozen in time. Each piece of petrified wood is one of a kind - the bezels for these stones were hand-fabricated in my studio to make these cufflinks. '),
(1660, 61, 0, 461, 'Lace agate is a beautiful banded form of cryptocrystalline quartz. Each piece of agate is individual, uniquely formed by nature. \r\n\r\nThis pair of agates caught my eye when I was at the Tucson gem shows. I like the lazy, winding patterns of the black, white and grey, that is softened by a few translucent brownish spots. I decided then that I would make them into cufflinks, and we hand-fabricated custom bezels for them in the studio. '),
(1661, 72, 0, 461, 'lace agate, onyx, cufflink, cufflinks, handmade, sterling silver, custom jewellery, toronto, canada'),
(1662, 62, 0, 461, 'Lace agate is a beautiful banded form of cryptocrystalline quartz. Each piece of agate is individual, uniquely formed by nature. \r\n\r\nThis pair of agates caught my eye when I was at the Tucson gem shows. I like the lazy, winding patterns of the black, white and grey, that is softened by a few translucent brownish spots. I decided then that I would make them into cufflinks, and we hand-fabricated custom bezels for them in the studio. '),
(1663, 61, 0, 462, 'Bloodstone is the mineral heliotrope, also known as Jasper. It is a type of quartz that is characterized by its distinctive black, red and green colouration. \r\n\r\nBloodstone has been used for carving signet rings and other objects since antiquity, and legends accord it many magical powers. Bloodstone is also one of the traditional birthstones for March.\r\n\r\nI was attracted to these colourful pieces of bloodstone at the Tucson gem shows because I liked the balance of the red black and green in them. I brought them back with me and we hand-fabricated them into sterling silver cufflinks in my studio in Toronto.'),
(1664, 72, 0, 462, 'handmade, sterling silver, bloodstone, jasper, heliotrope, cufflinks, birthstone, march, jewellery, toronto, canada'),
(1665, 62, 0, 462, 'I was attracted to these colourful pieces of bloodstone at the Tucson gem shows because I liked the balance of the red black and green in them. I brought them back with me and we hand-fabricated them into sterling silver cufflinks in my studio in Toronto.'),
(1666, 61, 0, 463, 'Everyone who wears cufflinks needs a couple of classic go-to shapes that will go with everything. These cufflinks will quickly become one of your favourites. \r\n\r\nTo add colour, we use a special metal paint on a textured background that is far more durable than stone. Shown here in blue and black, these cufflinks come in any colour and can be oriented on the cuff to either be a diamond shape (shown in blue) or on the square (shown in black). \r\n\r\nOf course, we can customize them to match almost any colour, which means they make wonderful corporate gifts, and are also perfect for weddings.\r\n\r\nAlso available in gold.'),
