(1681, 61, 0, 468, 'We had so much fun making these cufflinks! \r\n\r\nA woman approached us with a very special custom cufflink request. She had a sonogram of her baby\'s heartbeat, and an envelope inside of which was a piece of paper with the sex of the baby. \r\n\r\nShe asked us to make a pair of custom cufflinks with the sonogram engraved on them, and to put one of two gemstone colours into the top corner depending on the sex of the baby. \r\n\r\nShe then picked them up without looking into the box and she and her partner opened them together. It was a wonderful surprise and we enjoyed helping her pull it off! '),
