(1800, 61, 0, 508, 'Agate is one of the oldest gemstones in recorded history and is found in many colours in the earth\'s crust. It is a variety of chalcedony, a form of cryptocrystalline quartz, which is made up of crystal structures so fine they cannot be seen even under most magnification. \r\n\r\nDue to their ancient nature, agates have a great deal of significance as a healing crystal. Agates are typically thought to provide protection against various threats, including nightmares, stress and exhaustion. White agate is thought to offer an especially pure form of protection because of its “pure” colour.\r\n\r\nThis knotted strand of white agate consists of 10 mm round beads, with a 10 mm sterling silver ball clasp and measures approximately 18 inches.  \r\n'),
(1801, 72, 0, 508, 'agate, round, ball, clasp, knotted, necklace, gift, anniversary, mothers day, jewellery, toronto, jewelry'),
